{"PageNumber":0,"Angle":0,"RotatedAngle":0,"Height":2526,"Width":1785,"OriginHeight":0,"OriginWidth":0,"Elements":[{"Index":0,"Type":"title","Text":"#  3.博客后台","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":225,"Y":246},"LeftTop":{"X":225,"Y":187},"RightBottom":{"X":488,"Y":246},"RightTop":{"X":488,"Y":187}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":1,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"博客后台采用基于角色的访问控制模型，即RBAC (Role-Based Access Control)。RBAC 是当前系统开发中较为主流且常用的权限管理方案，主要通过“用户—角色—权限”之间的关联关系，实现对系统操作权限的统一管理。","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":224,"Y":417},"LeftTop":{"X":224,"Y":283},"RightBottom":{"X":1566,"Y":417},"RightTop":{"X":1566,"Y":283}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":2,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● 用户：系统的实际使用者，对应具体的账号或人员，例如张三、李四等。","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":249,"Y":488},"LeftTop":{"X":249,"Y":450},"RightBottom":{"X":1211,"Y":488},"RightTop":{"X":1211,"Y":450}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":3,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● 角色：用户在系统中的身份或职责划分，例如编辑、审核员、超级管理员等。","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":249,"Y":536},"LeftTop":{"X":249,"Y":493},"RightBottom":{"X":1270,"Y":536},"RightTop":{"X":1270,"Y":493}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":4,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"●权限:用户可执行的具体操作，例如查看文章、编辑文章、删除账号、管理用户等。","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":249,"Y":581},"LeftTop":{"X":249,"Y":539},"RightBottom":{"X":1361,"Y":581},"RightTop":{"X":1361,"Y":539}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":5,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"在 RBAC 权限管理方式中，一个用户可以绑定一个或多个角色；一个角色也可以关联多个权限。用户最终拥有的权限 = 所绑定角色的权限集合。例如，给用户张三分配“编辑”角色，而“编辑”角色拥有“查看文章”和“编写文章”权限，那么张三登录系统后便自动拥有这两项权限。","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":224,"Y":741},"LeftTop":{"X":224,"Y":614},"RightBottom":{"X":1548,"Y":741},"RightTop":{"X":1548,"Y":614}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":6,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"通过这种设计方式，权限管理更加清晰、灵活。当系统需要调整某类用户的操作权限时，只需修改对应角色的权限配置，所有绑定该角色的用户都会自动生效，无需逐个修改用户权限，从而降低了维护成本，提高了权限管理效率。","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":224,"Y":907},"LeftTop":{"X":224,"Y":773},"RightBottom":{"X":1548,"Y":907},"RightTop":{"X":1548,"Y":773}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":7,"Type":"figure","Text":"","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":545,"Y":1804},"LeftTop":{"X":545,"Y":933},"RightBottom":{"X":1273,"Y":1804},"RightTop":{"X":1273,"Y":933}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":[{"Index":0,"Type":"figure_text","Text":"graph TD     A[admin用户：完整权限] --> B[首页]     B --> C[写博文]     C --> D[系统管理]     D --> E[用户管理]     E --> F[角色管理]     F --> G[菜单管理]     G --> H[内容管理]     H --> I[分类管理]     H --> J[文章管理]     J --> K[分类管理]     K --> L[友链管理]     L --> M[标签管理]","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":545,"Y":1804},"LeftTop":{"X":545,"Y":933},"RightBottom":{"X":1273,"Y":1804},"RightTop":{"X":1273,"Y":933}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":0,"group_type":""}],"ImagePath":"images/2f0fc0d209ee7d369e6595d1a8b19b23-image.png","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":8,"Type":"title","Text":"##  3.1准备工作","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":224,"Y":1898},"LeftTop":{"X":224,"Y":1850},"RightBottom":{"X":479,"Y":1898},"RightTop":{"X":479,"Y":1850}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":9,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"1. 在后台模块 admin 的项目所在包下创建启动类 AdminApplication","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":258,"Y":1981},"LeftTop":{"X":258,"Y":1938},"RightBottom":{"X":1145,"Y":1981},"RightTop":{"X":1145,"Y":1938}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":10,"Type":"code","Text":"```\n@SpringBootApplication\n  public class AdminApplication {\n        public static void main(String[] args) {\n            SpringApplication.run(AdminApplication.class, args);}\n  }\n```","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":299,"Y":2244},"LeftTop":{"X":299,"Y":2034},"RightBottom":{"X":1293,"Y":2244},"RightTop":{"X":1293,"Y":2034}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":11,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"2. 在后台模块 admin 的 resources 目录下创建 application.yml 配置文件 (可从blog模块中复制，修改端口号为8989)","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":258,"Y":2388},"LeftTop":{"X":258,"Y":2302},"RightBottom":{"X":1561,"Y":2388},"RightTop":{"X":1561,"Y":2302}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""}]}